RSI really measures (intuition first)
RSI answers one question:
“Have prices gone up too fast or down too fast recently?”

Too much down → oversold → possible bounce
Too much up → overbought → possible drop

RSI range:
0 ───────── 100

- Step 0: Closing prices (real numbers)
| Day | Close |
| --: | ----: |
|   1 |   100 |
|   2 |   102 |
|   3 |   101 |
|   4 |   103 |
|   5 |   104 |
